<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mt-6 mb-2">Example 1 — Salary Raise</h3>
<div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6 shadow-sm">
  <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">This is the one most people care about. If you want to know <span class="font-semibold text-slate-800">how to calculate percentage raise on salary</span>, this is your example.</p>
  <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4"><span class="font-semibold text-slate-800">The situation:</span> You made $45,000 last year. You got a promotion. Now you make $54,000. You want to know what percentage raise you actually got.</p>
